You‚Äôll use AI to help you generate clear audience segments, meaning groups of people who are most likely to want your product or service.
You‚Äôll use the prompt below to generate 3 strong segments, based on how your product helps people and what needs it solves.
Once you‚Äôve done that, we‚Äôll move on to the next step: verifying that those audiences are actually being targeted by real brands.

