Purpose:
Create clear messages for your audience by linking their problems to how your product solves them.

Instructions:
In this step you‚Äôll use AI to find out what problems your audience segments struggle with and how your product or service solves them.
This is how you create messaging that actually gets results ‚Äî because it‚Äôs built on what people truly care about.
Instead of guessing what to say on your homepage or in your ads, you‚Äôll craft every word around real problems, real desires, and real data.
That‚Äôs what makes people stop, pay attention, and take action.

